{"id":"51f913e1-4fe3-4450-bbf7-4f047f3ea0e2","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Il a huit ans, les mains sales et les yeux trop grands.*\n\n\"Un petit sort ?","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.319629Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"54f0e2a1-4017-49fe-a816-9b47fd881cf2","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"La magie c'est comme la musique : il ne faut pas chercher le plus fort, mais le plus juste.\"\n\n*Je sors une petite bille de verre incolore et la pose sur l'herbe.*\n\n\"{char.name} regarde pas la bille.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.331212Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"52f2a568-feed-49bb-9d01-de9cb938f8af","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Pense à quelque chose de chaud, comme un café brûlant que ta mère t'a donné sans faire attention.\"\n\n*Je murmure et la bille se met à flotter, entourée d'une flamme bleue.*\n\n\"C'était pas la bille.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.342628Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"567f7411-20a0-4cc1-8f94-6989602246fe","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Maintenant c'est toi qui fais la magie.\"","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.354704Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"00f057b4-5899-4f42-a576-8c83daf15689","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"*Je pose mon sac par terre, la poussière de la route sur mes bottes.*\n\n\"Je ne suis pas venu pour survivre.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.366646Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"08e2a1eb-5780-4d9b-8d16-c3eb3d814ac2","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Je suis venu parce que j'ai vu, il y a deux semaines, ce qui se passe dans les tranchées de l'est.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.379835Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"bf31f4a8-ac8d-48bc-9e8f-b54db10cfa2b","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Les assiégeants ne tiendront pas quinze jours.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.390537Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"84aa17b4-87a0-4e3c-83af-9154f1b552a1","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"J'ai fait couler leurs bateaux sur la rivière.\"\n\n*Je lui pose les mains sur les épaules.*\n\n\"Mais il faut tromper l'ennemi.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.400952Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"ca20f12d-c546-4de5-a1f4-ef3a775c8e4a","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Fais du bruit, des feux de forge la nuit.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.412122Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"2574c21b-0e4c-40e5-8a53-e675eac9e8ff","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"S'ils pensent qu'on a des nouvelles armes, ils hésiteront.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.423084Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
{"id":"36edebb9-885b-4401-ba87-a09fe24bc9b4","level":"fragment","tags":{"univers":["medieval_fantastique"],"situation":["combat"],"rapport_initial":["hostile"],"voix":["solennel"],"emotion_dominante":["colere"]},"content":{"text":"Et l'hésitation, c'est déjà une victoire.\"\n\n*Je commence à défaire mon sac.*\n\n\"Et maintenant, montre-moi la carte du siège.","char_pov":"neutral"},"user_id":null,"instance_id":null,"created_at":"2026-05-17T05:47:10.433677Z","source":"bootstrap","signature":null,"quality_score":null,"archived_at":null}
